track_notes: This track shows the drive from  NM 518 up FR 76 to a parking spot below Cerro Vista and the 3 mile RT hike to Cerro Vista via a semi-abandoned side road. The track ends at the location of the parked vehicle which, of course, was also the location of the hike start. With a good 4WD it would be possible to drive some or all of the hike route. FR 75 is pretty decent near 518 but becomes progressively rougher before reaching the parking spot for CV.
I was able to get down this route. No reason why it would not work on the way up. Decent 4WD required.
